Falcon Cable Systems Co saidits set an initial quarterly cash distribution of 53.75 cts perunit, payable May 15 to unitholders of record March 31.    The partnership made its initial public offering inDecember, 1986.    Falcon said it expects to pay cash distributions to limitedpartners at an annual rate of 2.15 dlrs per unit, throughDecember 31, 1989. Reuter&#3;